# Zoom Clone — Project Context

Turborepo + pnpm monorepo. Two apps:

- `apps/web` — Next.js 16 (App Router), React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind v4, shadcn/ui
- `apps/api` — FastAPI, SQLAlchemy 2, Pydantic v2, WebSockets, SQLite (→ PostgreSQL)

## Code Standards

- No comments that narrate what the code does — comments explain _why_, not _what_
- Separate concerns: UI in `components/`, logic in `lib/`/`hooks/`, routes in `routers/`
- Reuse before rebuild — check existing utilities and components first
- No `any` in TypeScript; no bare `except` in Python

## Development Phases

- Phase 1: Monorepo scaffold ✅
- Phase 2: Dashboard UI + Meeting CRUD APIs
- Phase 3: Meeting room layout + camera preview
- Phase 4+: WebRTC mesh, host controls, JWT auth, Redis, PostgreSQL
